# RUST REWRITE

The python code is good and simple, but I'm interested in reducing the need for Python and etc.


## DESIGN

Use a client/server so the TMUX plugin can get the latest state without delay,
    and the server can run in the background.

Use shared memory and daemonize the server so the client can get the values immediately,
    and other clients can reuse the server.

A good candiate for the daemon would be systemd but I don't always have systemd installed,
    so I'm opting for a little more manual control.


